{
  "logNo": "222792255280",
  "title": "무릎의 움직임에 대하여. 무릎이 아플 때 고려해야 할 사항",
  "addDate": "2022. 6. 28.",
  "categoryNo": "21",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=222792255280",
  "html_size": 227563,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eddbd6a7-4150-422f-a2ea-6fdd5021ac64\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-bd47e245-6918-4385-b820-81b73f479a31\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3bb0a89e-51fe-49b7-b5ef-54bc29f406d8\">무릎을 완전히 펼 때 정강이뼈(경골 Tibia)가 약간 바깥쪽으로 회전(외회전 External rotation)하게 됩니다. 이를 screw-home 기전이라 부르죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-b699b61f-d922-4c4c-8607-a0714840d6a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e604fc5b-7c66-45bc-b4e2-87b760f357b7\">정강이뼈가 약간 외회전되면서 무릎 관절이 딱! 잠기는 듯이 맞아지게 되고, 서있을 때 무릎이 잠기면 체중이 허벅지뼈에서 정강이뼈로 효율적으로 전달이 되면서 근육에 힘을 주지 않고도 서있는 자세를 유지할 수 있게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-4a4e8f4e-a08d-4a8c-a4cc-e7d888629b92\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7eebc15c-555d-4ad9-862e-25e0da02ec6b\">무릎을 완전히 펴는 과정에서 전방십자인대(Anterior Cruciate ligament)에 의한 장력, 허벅지뼈(대퇴골 Femur) 끝 무릎 관절 모양의 내외측 비대칭에 의한 정강이뼈의 외회전움직임, 대퇴사두근 외측에서의 당기는 힘 등이 복합적으로 작용해서 Screw-home 현상이 이루어지게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-9725b2ae-32d2-40ab-a346-84476c8e4dd5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d163dcd9-09b2-41d4-b26d-1af85b229a71\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-3a42c438-0eb2-40da-8b54-3fd31572d35c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a2109e9a-2b66-4f4c-a45f-1bb935634914\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-894bf64f-c8bd-43be-8b81-6705e371c61d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:466px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-894bf64f-c8bd-43be-8b81-6705e371c61d\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA4/MDAxNjU2Mzk5Nzk5OTg0.dx8T6io6nfm3dqYj21BtE9xdgJSGQT-vcNdSrJDK6MIg.qCZHRFJBxdkLalHts4zEKVVbB1X9YL1-l2qOZ-LMCu4g.PNG.isuhani/screw_home.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"466\", \"originalHeight\" : \"357\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA4/MDAxNjU2Mzk5Nzk5OTg0.dx8T6io6nfm3dqYj21BtE9xdgJSGQT-vcNdSrJDK6MIg.qCZHRFJBxdkLalHts4zEKVVbB1X9YL1-l2qOZ-LMCu4g.PNG.isuhani/screw_home.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA4/MDAxNjU2Mzk5Nzk5OTg0.dx8T6io6nfm3dqYj21BtE9xdgJSGQT-vcNdSrJDK6MIg.qCZHRFJBxdkLalHts4zEKVVbB1X9YL1-l2qOZ-LMCu4g.PNG.isuhani/screw_home.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"466\" data-height=\"357\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a3a04356-90e1-4e99-9188-fa285a5da19f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-91fbcb50-ae27-4508-8246-2256af340eac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae02c0b4-e347-493a-9e9a-697380f988cd\">반대로 무릎을 구부릴 때는, screw-home 이 풀려야 하겠죠? 무릎 굴곡(구부림 flexion)을 시작하려면 정강이뼈가 약간 안쪽으로 회전(내회전 Internal rotation)해야 구부리는 동작이 가능해집니다. 무릎 뒤쪽, 오금에 있는 슬와근(Popliteus)라는 근육이 정강이뼈를 내회전 시키는 역할을 맡고 있어요. 아래 그림에서 보면 슬와근이 무릎을 구부릴 때 ‘Unlock’하는 기능을 한다고 설명하고 있죠. 쭉 펴진 무릎관절은 screw-home 현상에 의해 locking(잠김)되어 있다고 하고, 슬와근이 수축하면서 그 잠김을 풀어주는(unlock) 겁니다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-891d6d4d-1972-44c6-8b1c-bcee49f777b4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a04350fa-1f93-482a-988c-27964a877e18\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c352a373-4399-4379-86ed-1b3960918a4c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c352a373-4399-4379-86ed-1b3960918a4c\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA2/MDAxNjU2Mzk5ODIyMDU3.Qr73B9WA4ET7d5AU31yzVlfN34eKzN96je2oPxkTBl0g.oiSqqVTdfiVXGD9Fx1eIHI4Wm2bRYke_UN-Ukn1vvPkg.JPEG.isuhani/popliteus_unlock.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"940\", \"originalHeight\" : \"669\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA2/MDAxNjU2Mzk5ODIyMDU3.Qr73B9WA4ET7d5AU31yzVlfN34eKzN96je2oPxkTBl0g.oiSqqVTdfiVXGD9Fx1eIHI4Wm2bRYke_UN-Ukn1vvPkg.JPEG.isuhani/popliteus_unlock.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA2/MDAxNjU2Mzk5ODIyMDU3.Qr73B9WA4ET7d5AU31yzVlfN34eKzN96je2oPxkTBl0g.oiSqqVTdfiVXGD9Fx1eIHI4Wm2bRYke_UN-Ukn1vvPkg.JPEG.isuhani/popliteus_unlock.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"355\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3c1efc6-a62f-4d4b-b8ad-1eee6ff88586\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-7c110f8c-38ba-42df-b84b-5c61b2c240e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dcf63764-2b54-4ce6-8b4c-41590856ee2e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-dcab6c2f-67aa-4572-9f58-054874abcda2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62c57a66-efa3-4b3b-9c55-328ede0fe76f\">무릎을 구부리고 펴는 동작에 이러한 무릎관절의 회전은 나름 중요한 역할을 하는거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-ff6c3c20-fdd1-4b8c-a2ad-9967049f08e4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ab92aae1-d5cf-442c-8010-17fca6fda9cf\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-ecdbe25e-f855-4361-a768-2ee63017acc7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e38a0ad4-b8da-4207-9929-957f40693099\">우리가 걸음을 걷는 과정에서는 발이 지면에 닿을 때 발생하는 안쪽 기울어짐(회내 Pronation. 발의 ‘엎침’이라고 번역하기도 합니다)에 의해 정강이뼈가 내회전 되면서 아주 자연스럽게 신전과 굴곡이 이루어지게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-2e879535-7c0c-4091-ae1e-1bdeb60f5531\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2e4366a0-8a0f-439b-9e62-b628f2830f1a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-41b62f30-5adc-4c74-8a91-f64bea4ed593\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39379dfd-5cce-400e-95b1-e2943f578b75\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-62b9ac90-f08b-47cc-95bb-6b63ad484847\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-62b9ac90-f08b-47cc-95bb-6b63ad484847\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA0/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTc5ODcz.t9xLsyaOEzDmahRqOSnsMM5ESnOSQjzXY56xA_oFaQAg.gyqJgvX82zkmNiufmO12yqM8EL_D5mJd7hAbjmFe_nwg.PNG.isuhani/normal_gait_cycle.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"602\", \"originalHeight\" : \"141\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA0/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTc5ODcz.t9xLsyaOEzDmahRqOSnsMM5ESnOSQjzXY56xA_oFaQAg.gyqJgvX82zkmNiufmO12yqM8EL_D5mJd7hAbjmFe_nwg.PNG.isuhani/normal_gait_cycle.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTA0/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTc5ODcz.t9xLsyaOEzDmahRqOSnsMM5ESnOSQjzXY56xA_oFaQAg.gyqJgvX82zkmNiufmO12yqM8EL_D5mJd7hAbjmFe_nwg.PNG.isuhani/normal_gait_cycle.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"117\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f78a4db1-acdd-42af-a6ad-703af13d7020\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-9487ec48-efb5-40f2-9ceb-f914c7a123ff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6f4246bd-3da6-49d3-8097-21aefcefe926\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-24e6ee34-7da2-4602-ba04-1c8c9814d707\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-61a0e702-9862-47ca-867a-7e0fa6894876\">위 그림은 정상 보행 단계(Normal Gait Cycle)를 표현한 그림입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-1c528472-5f95-400d-85b5-4ba058b60afd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-963fc8d0-b437-4388-ba2c-aa7defb2b7a0\">보행의 첫 단계는 앞으로 내딛는 발의 뒷꿈치가 땅에 닫는 순간이죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-97df5304-0f02-4e0f-8fae-10c77e09bb4e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0a2b845-e7b6-4cad-9d2c-85eeb0c6fbc4\">이 순간을 Heelstrike(뒷꿈치 닿기)라고 합니다. Heelstrike 순간에는 무릎이 완전히 쭉 펴져있습니다. 무릎이 쭉 펴지면 screw-home 현상으로 무릎관절이 잠기게 되겠죠? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-4aa6a120-1ad4-46b0-8079-7760e5854945\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f0ccd50b-7188-48f1-aba6-2e7d781755e4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-94d3aec1-34d3-4857-870d-feafba03064f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a9aec57-8f89-409e-8c92-4c6950e0adca\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe445374-3774-4586-b1b0-919f5bb909fb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:451px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fe445374-3774-4586-b1b0-919f5bb909fb\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMzgg/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTk2MzYw.JGZprMT7Ydk7mxtD8MSuAGvGBb1CTvn7_psAbvHiHYog.prX13L2vUNXE4NW8OyFOlJnBfaI1h1_zXk-K5vLge6wg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_phase.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"451\", \"originalHeight\" : \"338\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMzgg/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTk2MzYw.JGZprMT7Ydk7mxtD8MSuAGvGBb1CTvn7_psAbvHiHYog.prX13L2vUNXE4NW8OyFOlJnBfaI1h1_zXk-K5vLge6wg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_phase.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMzgg/MDAxNjU2Mzk5OTk2MzYw.JGZprMT7Ydk7mxtD8MSuAGvGBb1CTvn7_psAbvHiHYog.prX13L2vUNXE4NW8OyFOlJnBfaI1h1_zXk-K5vLge6wg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_phase.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"451\" data-height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2433d177-2cb4-4886-b409-9834db1ad6c6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-407b0b1c-0e47-4edd-b319-714a6fdc0c18\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-409bc6cc-3122-435d-8211-59c6c7815c63\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-b0abce07-fc15-49e5-9d79-60dde8cdb8c1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-49c1c74f-919f-4035-824e-d76312d30301\">Healstrike 단계에서 잠기는 무릎관절은 발이 회내(Pronation)되면서 정강이뼈의 내회전을 유발하고 자연스럽게 무릎의 굴곡이 이루어질 수 있게 잠김을 풀어줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-7111b18b-d3bc-402e-85d3-c3e7629620c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-220f170d-82c1-4f34-890b-39b0d4797771\">반대로 발을 밀어내는 Push off(또는 Toe off, Pre-swing, Prolulsive phase) 단계에서는 발이 회외(Supination)되면서 정강이뼈의 외회전(External rotation)이 생기면서 무릎이 펴지는 걸 돕게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-e3dc2b64-23db-4d6c-87f9-121132061a40\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6011ad31-d5c2-4566-91af-60ef531e34e5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-collage\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-collage\" id=\"SE-3ca04f65-5c0f-4a91-ab69-611c114998a4\">\n                            <div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n                                <div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n                                    \n                                    <div class=\"se-imageGroup-item se-imageGroup-col-2\">\n                                    <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"width:81.74741736035419%;\">\n                                        <a href=\"#\" id=\"SE-c8176368-8a4b-412b-9337-f56d996c8444\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c8176368-8a4b-412b-9337-f56d996c8444\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMjcy/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDIwOTM4.-ltsPJWXbA98z4u-FLSirzlJRHiVwEkcbaB-BDBm9rUg._1actnvTJ1OYUnPt0Gehmj_QQPKnQDNt8VZ6dD7-vKcg