12-921e5107de66\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7c5b69cc-d05e-4fd7-bacd-e5636c259bbc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7c5b69cc-d05e-4fd7-bacd-e5636c259bbc\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfNCAg/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDMxNjA4.3gbzVFgmTlZlfzNR5Ep58CzbiTJOxTuT5Cezst-5Tfwg.tx7PsKrJ58FmP4Hl0S_PwxSb6mSLxQrA02rphdsS5KUg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_foot.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"625\", \"originalHeight\" : \"471\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfNCAg/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDMxNjA4.3gbzVFgmTlZlfzNR5Ep58CzbiTJOxTuT5Cezst-5Tfwg.tx7PsKrJ58FmP4Hl0S_PwxSb6mSLxQrA02rphdsS5KUg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_foot.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfNCAg/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDMxNjA4.3gbzVFgmTlZlfzNR5Ep58CzbiTJOxTuT5Cezst-5Tfwg.tx7PsKrJ58FmP4Hl0S_PwxSb6mSLxQrA02rphdsS5KUg.JPEG.isuhani/gait_foot.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"376\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a9811bc7-ed54-4c5b-bae3-350ec64dd6cd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-5a282ba0-be20-4b22-b609-b4f6165cde11\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3633540c-0f18-4c9b-bb35-c74413f4f501\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-ecd078f5-652e-4295-8775-2fce23debb2f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0475d3d-f832-41ca-b768-569517055f09\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-6e9bac27-7893-4661-8e3b-45c5414e5019\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a4d4dce1-d56b-41c8-8daa-a094e125ae9e\">건강한 사람은 앉고 설 때, 무릎을 굽히고 펴는데 아무런 문제가 없으니 의식적인 노력 없이도 쉽게 구부리고, 쉽게 펼 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-6a056a63-d4b4-46a9-8ee1-280aaf242d63\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-026cfcb1-0955-4c81-b0c7-4fe6964c8b73\">보행을 할 때도 정상 보행 단계에 따라 다리가, 발목이 자동으로 움직이는 듯이 자연스럽게 움직이면서 무릎을 구부리게 되고 펴게 되죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-e3b3becc-0c52-45b1-ba98-438948385c92\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-de46bce9-99c9-499e-ae83-dfb945423477\">그러나 근육에 이상이 있거나, 관절의 퇴행이 있거나 근육과 관절에 대한 신경조절이 제대로 이루어지지 못하게 되면 무릎을 펴고 구부리는게 뜻대로 되지 않고, 걸음걸이가 불편해지게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-274f6f4d-c82e-42f3-a8ed-123bd59df9e8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-006f925a-3403-41cd-9401-dd66387727ce\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-f4f0130c-8fc3-4e7d-853c-7ae59496f601\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-98558c53-d9c0-46fa-a066-b6208e8c4c68\">노화 또는 질병 등으로 뇌기능이 저하되면서 신경조절이 적절히 이루어지지 않을 때에도 걸음걸이가 이상해지죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-c2e8f0bc-8049-402b-9991-8749b43963cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b1281fad-be40-4eaf-ad0c-33c231a493dc\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-10ca65b0-344d-42bb-8248-33ce9f81b0e8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0bc48b3-645f-447f-8ea9-74b8c758e3d7\">무릎관절을 치료할 때, 관절 역학적인 부분들을 고려해서 문제점을 파악하고 치료해야하고, 보행에 관여하는 다른 부분(오늘 포스팅에서는 발목의 회내, 회외 움직임)들도 고려해야 합니다. 발목 뿐 아니고 고관절의 움직임, 허리와 골반 사이의 움직임도 영향을 주니 그 부분에 대한 점검도 필요하죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-ffaa7a7a-b6e4-418a-a470-d9dc24315cde\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-092e9068-af9e-480c-9ca1-e1edc76130b9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-f7e0daa2-c64e-4853-84ec-0e5191659b9d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bbf3c7b4-6321-49ff-9739-3da58319cafb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-a2bd74a5-2802-4335-bd03-604d8c17a4eb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c9143003-9012-4ba6-8fd2-a6a4a395a142\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-0501e662-d626-4252-9907-03e3f5e29c26\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-51b1d0af-1074-4c02-af37-feeab7163e11\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-1f26788a-e8fc-45b2-9682-5f03634d44af\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d9a362eb-d8b7-4584-92c0-058219d91b55\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-4229e370-c6b3-4d2d-91ce-7148af22d301\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6cc6c90b-e7a4-41c2-9144-439502186c66\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-29d1e3e5-018d-4eb1-a2cb-97a123975fac\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:323px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-29d1e3e5-018d-4eb1-a2cb-97a123975fac\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMjcy/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDQ3ODYx.MD8K_sKPferYU0-6UmxVCwvIYckUAH04AQjw6F-kTlwg.DdF8fNnkzGsdZ_6ThzubotE_j2cDnKHmwfGxbdc59bkg.JPEG.isuhani/foot.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"323\", \"originalHeight\" : \"169\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMjcy/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDQ3ODYx.MD8K_sKPferYU0-6UmxVCwvIYckUAH04AQjw6F-kTlwg.DdF8fNnkzGsdZ_6ThzubotE_j2cDnKHmwfGxbdc59bkg.JPEG.isuhani/foot.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMjcy/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDQ3ODYx.MD8K_sKPferYU0-6UmxVCwvIYckUAH04AQjw6F-kTlwg.DdF8fNnkzGsdZ_6ThzubotE_j2cDnKHmwfGxbdc59bkg.JPEG.isuhani/foot.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"323\" data-height=\"169\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4e54481a-dc20-4cc2-b029-ae6dec663cc7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-00e7ce57-bc15-4517-879e-bb0c48c7850e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b850b91-b441-4823-8cb8-a7df94d20663\">여담으로, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-c20c8a46-f0f0-4df6-beff-e6e5d34ff04d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b64f31fc-7ff5-4af8-be7c-707365c356f4\">간단하게 본다면, 보행을 할 때 발바닥에 실리는 체중은 위 그림의 검은 선을 따라서 이동하게 됩니다. Healstrike 단계에서 뒷꿈치 중앙에 실려있던 체중은 발목관절의 회외(무릎을 곧게 펴는 동작과 연관됩니다)와 더불어 뒷꿈이 바깥쪽(새끼발가락 쪽)으로 옮겨갔다가 발목관절의 회내(무릎을 구부리는 동작과 연관됩니다)와 더불어 발바닥의 중심을 지나 엄지발가락 쪽으로 이동하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-3dc2c15a-08a9-4ab5-9f9d-15bba4e6e1bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85743e3a-b666-497c-b34b-bf67024dfafa\">러닝을 위한 운동화의 밑창은 이런 발의 역학적 움직임을 고려해서 만들어집니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-744baa2d-d294-451a-92fa-6f0ad45c6f3a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-96f8a947-0f6e-4642-b501-a5e45898ffea\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-246fbf4a-7139-4442-883b-aaedafac370f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-246fbf4a-7139-4442-883b-aaedafac370f\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTIx/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDU5OTg4.Lrxsz6dxhZRU42A4tF8UvEAMnpRVFuLtsdnXyMKPFCQg.M9JEmGPcSjxFVJNmxnWbEdZaBqMV8P0O7TBIlfdLXs4g.PNG.isuhani/%EC%8B%A0%EB%B0%9C_%EB%B0%91%EC%B0%BD.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"559\", \"originalHeight\" : \"306\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTIx/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDU5OTg4.Lrxsz6dxhZRU42A4tF8UvEAMnpRVFuLtsdnXyMKPFCQg.M9JEmGPcSjxFVJNmxnWbEdZaBqMV8P0O7TBIlfdLXs4g.PNG.isuhani/%EC%8B%A0%EB%B0%9C_%EB%B0%91%EC%B0%BD.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA2MjhfMTIx/MDAxNjU2NDAwMDU5OTg4.Lrxsz6dxhZRU42A4tF8UvEAMnpRVFuLtsdnXyMKPFCQg.M9JEmGPcSjxFVJNmxnWbEdZaBqMV8P0O7TBIlfdLXs4g.PNG.isuhani/%EC%8B%A0%EB%B0%9C_%EB%B0%91%EC%B0%BD.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-